cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.NE

The paper proposes a parallel algorithm for causal structure learning, which is a problem in machine learning and statistics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves parallel computing, which suggests it could belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Additionally, the paper uses statistical methods, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
